Class EditMomentPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture

          • com.pom.crimson.pages.EditMomentPage

  • public class EditMomentPage
extends AddNewMomentsPage
    Edit moment page can be used to edit moments for primary profile or child profiles.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Go to Home Page
    Click "Moments log" widget
    Click "Add new moment" link
    Create a moment
    Once moment is created,Tap on Moment and select "Edit moment"

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Jaspreet Kaur Chagger
